n Monday, said for the first time that instead of teams sailing down the Seine on barges, the ceremony could be \\\"limited to the Trocadero\\\" building across the river from the Eiffel Tower or \\\"even moved to the Stade de France\\\".\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 292, \"end\": 298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 0.9999999997223767, \"rank\": 2.775479975672169e-10, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 383, \"end\": 388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999145075, \"rank\": 6.866573342974753e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 318}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 343}, {\"ngram\": \"teams\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 365}, {\"ngram\": \"barges\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 398}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 412}, {\"ngram\": \"the Trocadero\\\" building\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 457}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 474}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"the Stade de France\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"READ:Macron says Olympic opening ceremony could move from river to stadium if security threat The Paris organisers have devised a ceremony that is unprecedented in Olympic history as it breaks from the tradition of the Games opening in the main stadium.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 0.9999999997223767, \"rank\": 2.775479975672169e-10, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999688498, \"rank\": 3.123057864563556e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic opening ceremony\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"river\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"security threat\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"a ceremony\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic history\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"the tradition\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games opening\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"the main stadium\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The current plans would see as many as 10,000 athletes sailing along a six-kilometre (four-mile) stretch of the Seine in around 160 barges, before gathering at the Trocadero for a ceremony.\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 983, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999145075, \"rank\": 6.866573342974753e-11, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The current plans\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"as many as 10,000 athletes\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"a six-kilometre (four-mile) stretch\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 898}, {\"ngram\": \"around 160 barges\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"the Trocadero\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"a ceremony\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 982}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But with war currently raging in Ukraine and in Gaza, concerns have been raised that the ceremony could leave athletes potentially vulnerable to attack.\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1018, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9962166665803743, \"rank\": 0.0037208175969991705, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 1033, \"end\": 1037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"score\": 0.9923513944963899, \"rank\": 0.007705814749263803, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"war\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"attack\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am clearly concerned,\\\" Anson told Sky News in an interview broadcast Wednesday to mark 100 days to go until the opening ceremony on July 26.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1165, \"end\": 1170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avro_Anson\", \"score\": 0.9999595559800311, \"rank\": 4.0444532631436645e-05, \"text\": \"Anson\", \"types\": [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avro_Anson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avro_Anson\"}, {\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News\", \"score\": 0.9999997936279428, \"rank\": 2.063698717518603e-07, \"text\": \"Sky News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interview broadcast\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"100 days\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1237}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's one of the most important things that we have to manage from a risk perspective.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most important things\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1322}, {\"ngram\": \"a risk perspective\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We'd be naive if we were not thinking about that.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our number one priority is to keep all our athletes, our broader entourage and our fans safe.\\\"\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our number one priority\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"all our athletes\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"our broader entourage\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"our fans\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anson added the opening ceremony \\\"is a high-risk environment and that's got to be managed accordingly, but the French are very, very aware of that\\\".\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1519, \"end\": 1524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avro_Anson\", \"score\": 0.9999595559800311, \"rank\": 4.0444532631436645e-05, \"text\": \"Anson\", \"types\": [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avro_Anson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avro_Anson\"}, {\"begin\": 1630, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.560017015118138, \"rank\": 0.7618669064955117, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the open